Jan 27 2008 	Hao Shie Shie Ni !	I stayed in this hotel right smack in the middle of winter January, 2008. I enjoyed my stay there. The staff were very attentive to my needs. They are always on hand to help with directions, they right down in chinese the direction for the cab driver. Evryone tries to speak english. The room was typical, clean and spacious. The breakfast buffet was laid out with a good selection of food. You can literally stuff yourself for the busy day ahead. Only drawback is the main shopping center is a cab away, a short one though. The location of Merry Mart right across is great for grocery needs. Overall, I would stay again in this hotel.	
